spell_list.description: Passively allows the warlock to build charges of Toxic Aura when using damage spells. The trigger chance on Toxic Aura is 33% at Rank 1, 66% at Rank 2 and 100% at Rank 3. Toxic Aura increments at 3 per attack target and maxes at 180. Toxic Assault inflicts disease damage to the warlock's target. The damage is substantially higher with 180 charges of Toxic Aura.
spell_list.description_pvp: Passively allows the warlock to build charges of Toxic Aura when using damage spells. The trigger chance on Toxic Aura is 33% at Rank 1, 66% at Rank 2 and 100% at Rank 3. Toxic Aura increments at 3 per attack target and maxes at 180. Toxic Assault inflicts disease damage to the warlock's target. The damage is substantially higher with 180 charges of Toxic Aura.

effect_list.description: Consumes all increments of Toxic Aura
You must have at least 10 increments of Toxic Aura to use Toxic Assault!

spell_list.name: Toxic Assault
